    <_name>LiveWallpaper Preferences</_name>
    <_summary>Configuration interfaces for LiveWallpaper</_summary>
    <description>
        <_p>
            This package provides two interfaces that permit you to configure 
            your LiveWallpaper.
        </_p>
        <_p>
            The first one is a full of options preference window. With it, you can
            manage LiveWallpaper as well as its installed plugins, an customize both
            of them without technical knowledge.
        </_p>
        <_p>
            The second one is an applet for your panel that allow you to start
            or stop LiveWallpaper, to select the active plugin, and to quickly 
            open the preferences window without passing by the menu.
        </_p>
    </description>
    
